cast.overview: When oil is discovered in 1920s Oklahoma under Osage Nation land, the Osage people are murdered one by one—until the FBI steps in to unravel the mystery.
cast.title: Killers of the Flower Moon

details.biography: Jennifer Rader is an Oklahoma Native and Native American member of the Sokaogon Chippewa tribe of Wisconsin. Formerly a professional dancer training in modern dance, ballet, tap, and hip hop, Jennifer has performed premiere works both nationally and internationally. A fierce dedication to the training, discipline, and considering herself an avid story teller, paved a direct path to exploring outlets and creating a passion for acting. She has appeared in the Oscar-Nominated film Killers of the Flower Moon, directed by Martin Scorsese, soon to premiere Twisters, and the biopic Reagan opposite Dennis Quaid.
details.name: Jennifer Rader
